<bibRefCitation author="Bellamy" box="[264,579,1236,1262]" pageId="10" pageNumber="27" refString="Bellamy, C. L. &amp; Nelson, G. H. (1989) Lectotype designations in the Buprestidae collections of the National Museum of Natural History (Coleoptera). Insecta Mundi, 3, 289 - 297." type="journal article" year="1989">
Bellamy and Nelson 
<number box="[516,579,1236,1262]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" value="1989.0">1989</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). A photograph of the 
<typeStatus box="[862,912,1236,1262]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11">type</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName authority="Duges" authorityName="Duges" box="[955,1268,1236,1262]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="caliginosus">
